data.description: Exceptional modern architectural design with an open floor plan. Premium Saratoga location/neighborhood. Large-scale remodel completed in 2008. Impressive designer materials used throughout to create the perfect modern California lifestyle home. High ceilings! Dramatic formal entry. Luxurious formal living room with fireplace. Spacious formal dining room. Stunning gourmet kitchen features custom cabinets, commercial grade appliances and large kitchen island. Kitchen opens to family great room with fireplace. Two gracious primary suites. All bathrooms have been beautifully remodeled. An abundance of natural light. The curb appeal is exceptional. Beautifully landscaped grounds. In-ground pool. Solar owned! Award winning schools. For those seeking the ultimate family home in which to live, this property will exceed expectations!
